d33 = Direction.create(direction: "Preheat the oven to 350 degrees F (175 degrees C). Lightly grease a 9x5-inch loaf pan.", ordinal: 0, recipe: r6)
d34 = Direction.create(direction: "Combine flour, baking soda, and salt in a large bowl. Beat brown sugar and butter with an electric mixer in a separate large bowl until smooth. Stir in eggs and mashed bananas until well blended. Stir banana mixture into flour mixture until just combined. Pour batter into the prepared loaf pan.", ordinal: 1, recipe: r6)
